1.  Aida (reseed)
2.  Boris Godunov
3.  Der Fliegende Hollander aka The Flying Dutchmen
4.  Die Fledermaus aka The Bat
5.  Fidelio
6.  Il Trovatore
7.  Lakme
8.  L'eliser d'amore aka The Elixer of Love
9.  Les Contes d'Hoffman aka The Tales of Hoffman
10. Lucia di Lammermoor
11. Manon Lescaut
12. Salome
13. Tannhauser (reseed)
14. The Mikado
